          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h4 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm">+10 a√±os</h4>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">Experiencia</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <a
    href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/carmen-acosta-091532153/"
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
    class=" left-1/2 w-full -translate-x-1/2 -bottom-18 sm:w-min sm:h-min   sm:translate-x-0 sm:left-[300px] sm:top-18 absolute group bg-gradient-to-r bg-primary text-white font-semibold p-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:shadow-blue-600/40 hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]"
  >
    <svg
      class="w-7 h-7 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
      fill="currentColor"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    >
      <path
